Now we are going to publish our project using "render.com". We will deploy our github
repository in it. We will connect it with the render, select region - southern asia
in the advance options, we will turn off auto deploy. and then we will create our deployment
In the deployment page, we will goto connect and copy all the IP's given and paste it in the
mongoAtlas security/"network access" add IP.

Then we will deploy our project manually by clicking on the "manual deploy" -> "clear log and deploy".

Hurray!! Deployment Done!!
